column1: # WITH scr AS (  SELECT DISTINCT observation::text AS observation_id,object::text AS sso_name  FROM sso.screening_output_raw  where "L" like 'Y' or "L" like 'D'),xmm AS (  SELECT    observation_id,    sso_name,    ra_deg_1, dec_deg_1,    ra_deg_2, dec_deg_2,    filter,    xmatch_type,    v_mag_1,    v_mag_1_corrected,    mlim_obs  FROM sso.xmm_om_unique WHERE filter = 'L') SELECT  x.observation_id,  x.sso_name,  x.ra_deg_1, x.dec_deg_1,  x.ra_deg_2, x.dec_deg_2,  x.filter,  x.xmatch_type,  x.v_mag_1,  x.v_mag_1_corrected,  x.mlim_obs FROM scr s JOIN xmm x  ON x.observation_id = s.observation_id AND x.sso_name       = s.sso_name
